{"tid":2379593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6.12一周年女子藏雷射筆被控 女警指神情閃縮繞道而行起疑截查","createTime":"2021-01-25T10:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:56:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbda73c4a1db0ad887648fe37d8c4989dd7bf0e9","tid":2379593,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"一名會計女文員在旺角街頭遇警截查，背囊被搜出雷射筆及「光時」旗幟等物品，被控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，審件今日在西九龍裁判法院開審。負責截查的女警供稱，<span class=\"red\">當日被告見到警察後神情閃縮，並繞過警員企圖離開。辯方則稱只因警方一行八人巡邏，被告才被迫繞道</span>。辯方並稱，當晚沒有人使用雷射筆，區內亦沒有人展示同類旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n盤問下，女警承認當晚沒有看見任何人使用雷射筆，亦沒有見過有人展示同類旗幟，被告沒有戴面巾或手套。涉案鐳射筆在內格底部搜出，她同意沒見過被告拿著或使用雷射筆，亦承認被告表現合作。"},{"pid":"8169fada0d134f36e2eb9780e37584f07d0cf8f9","tid":2379593,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/RXTISEEBMZHQZJUPNZNHR3MJJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FRXTISEEBMZHQZJUPNZNHR3MJJ4%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=8582c74e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FRXTISEEBMZHQZJUPNZNHR3MJJ4%2F&h=7493e31b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/RXTISEEBMZHQZJUPNZNHR3MJJ4/</a>"},{"pid":"f3ed589f34304d8a2a991ad6cce1d4e456379563","tid":2379593,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"屈得就屈 黑警特色"},{"pid":"539ec602a296c19cad2e06d0a5b45fcb6c05d38b","tid":2379593,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdaaf23766335a47a2f6b5fa95cb94b1fad3d65","tid":2379593,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite